 &lt;div class="callout-body">
 &lt;p>Oakestra achieves a flexible system architecture that empowers users to dynamically tailor the system to fit specific use cases while preserving a streamlined core.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hooks</title><link>oakestra.github.io/docs/concepts/oakestra-extensions/hooks/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>oakestra.github.io/docs/concepts/oakestra-extensions/hooks/</guid><description>&lt;span class="lead">
