 &lt;div class="callout-content">
 
 &lt;div class="callout-body">
 &lt;p>Unlike addons, which extend functionality by adding components, hooks enable services to listen and respond to the dynamic state changes of entities like applications or services within Oakestra.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Custom Resources</title><link>oakestra.github.io/docs/concepts/oakestra-extensions/custom-resources/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>oakestra.github.io/docs/concepts/oakestra-extensions/custom-resources/</guid><description>&lt;span class="lead">
